keyToStrMap.Full:
Travis the Trumpet Player

Occupation:
[] Trumpet player (previously town crier)

Likes:
[] Marching bands, playing football

Dislikes:
[] Rust, potholes

Favourite quote:
[] The road to success is not easy to navigate

Favourite people in the (living) world:
[] My pet canary

How I came to be here:
[] One day I just ran out of puff

What I wish:
[] To make trumpet playing cool again
